"translation api\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"user social profile tab\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=99213\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:495:\"<p>This year, we’re on a mission to add the most value to our plugin. That’s why we’re so excited to announce AIOSEO 4.2.2. In this update, we have a lot of exciting improvements, with the top two being: Social profile&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-our-new-user-social-profile-tab-and-translation-api-in-aioseo-4-2-2/\">Announcing Our New User Social Profile Tab and Translation API in AIOSEO 4.2.2</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Benjamin Rojas\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4769:\"<p>This year, we’re on a mission to add the most value to our plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s why we’re so excited to announce AIOSEO 4.2.2.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this update, we have a lot of exciting improvements, with the top two being:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Social profile management</li><li>Translation API</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>These are features designed to give your SEO a boost so you can get more traffic to your website. The best part is they’re easy to use, even if you’re a WordPress newbie.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s quickly dive into what this new update offers for AIOSEO users.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Easily Connect Your Social Media Profiles to Your Site</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The first feature we&#8217;re proud to introduce is the User Social Profile management feature. It makes it easy for you to connect your social media profiles to your WordPress user accounts – with just a few clicks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One reason we’re happy to announce this feature is that it’s one of the most-requested features by many of our users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To access this new feature, head over to your WordPress dashboard and click on <strong>Users</strong> &gt;&gt; <strong>Profile</strong>. This will take you to the User Profile page.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img width=\"431\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/social-profile-3.png\" alt=\"The new User Social Profile tab enables you to connect your social media accounts to your wordPress user account.\" class=\"wp-image-99561\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/social-profile-3.png 431w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/social-profile-3-300x278.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>You can then fill in the social media profiles you want associated with that user. For example, you can easily connect your Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, or any other social media account to your user profile.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you’re done, click <strong>Save</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This will result in your social media profiles being added to your site’s schema. Schema is a code that helps search engines understand your site better. Adding your social profiles has many advantages including boosting your:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Google E-A-T score</strong>: Expertise, authority, and trustworthiness (E-A-T) is a score Google uses to rate the quality of content on your site. Trustworthiness is an important element in getting a good E-A-T score. Connecting social profiles to your content improves the trust factor.</li><li><strong>Entity SEO</strong>: Entity SEO involves search engines using related data about an entity (person, business, or object) to build a better profile. This helps them serve relevant answers to queries related to said entity.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In short, this helps boost discoverability and results in more traffic to your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Localize Your SEO Data with the Translation API</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our brand new translation API is another reason we’re excited about AIOSEO 4.2.2. The translation API enables third-party translation apps to hook into AIOSEO’s data to translate it easily.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This helps users reach a wider audience. But more importantly, it helps boost your multilingual SEO. With our new translation API, you can rank for important keywords across different languages and geographic demographics.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Of course, that translates to more traffic to your website and faster growth for your business.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides these 2, we’ve updated many of the features you love in AIOSEO, such as improved:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Content optimization</li><li>The pre-publish panel that now includes a check for the social data</li><li>Link Suggestions</li><li>And much more!</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This update has lots of exciting additions and improvements to help your website rank higher, so make sure to update to AIOSEO 4.2.2 today.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/contact/\" title=\"Contact Us\">reach out to our customer support team here</a>, and they’ll be happy to help you out.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Go ahead and take advantage of the additional power of AIOSEO 4.2.2 by upgrading to a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">Pro or Elite plan</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As always, we value your feedback and input. That’s why we encourage you to keep the suggestions and feature requests coming. Together, we’ll build the world’s best WordPress SEO plugin and toolkit.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-our-new-user-social-profile-tab-and-translation-api-in-aioseo-4-2-2/\">Announcing Our New User Social Profile Tab and Translation API in AIOSEO 4.2.2</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:103:\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-our-new-user-social-profile-tab-and-translation-api-in-aioseo-4-2-2/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"11\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"16 Best Free WordPress Plugins You Need in 2022\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:118:\"https://aioseo.com/best-free-wordpress-plugins/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=best-free-wordpress-plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://aioseo.com/best-free-wordpress-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 20 Jun 2022 14:20:16 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"best free WordPress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"free WordPress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=12380\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:418:\"<p>Are you looking for the best free WordPress plugins? WordPress is the most popular website builder in the world, and it comes with 1000s of free and premium plugins. Because there are so many, it&#8217;s hard for a beginner to&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-free-wordpress-plugins/\">16 Best Free WordPress Plugins You Need in 2022</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45225:\"<p>Are you looking for the best free WordPress plugins?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress is the most popular <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-website-builder-for-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"website builder\">website builder</a> in the world, and it comes with 1000s of free and premium plugins.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because there are so many, it&#8217;s hard for a beginner to know which to choose!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Free WordPress plugins may not offer all the features of premium plugins, but they&#8217;re great for beginners getting started and businesses on a budget. Many free plugins have a premium version with more features, so you can always upgrade later as your business grows.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By using the free version, you’ll also be able to test out the plugin features and options. This way, you can easily decide whether you want to stick with the plugin or look for alternatives.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll share some of the best free WordPress plugins that you can use.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">AIOSEO</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is one of the best free WordPress plugins to consider for your site.\" class=\"wp-image-96547\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO) is a comprehensive SEO toolkit used on over 3 million websites. Many smart marketers trust AIOSEO to help them boost their visibility in search and drive traffic to their websites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When setting up your website, SEO is one of the most important factors to consider. While WordPress is SEO-friendly, there’s so much more you can do to give your website a competitive edge.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To do that, you need an SEO plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And one of the best WordPress SEO plugins on the market is AIOSEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Even with the free version, you’ll be able to configure your SEO settings and optimize your site for better rankings. And don’t worry, setting up AIOSEO is super easy as it comes with a handy setup wizard that will walk you through all the steps.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once configured, you’ll have access to many powerful features such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>On-page optimization</li><li>XML sitemaps</li><li>Woocommerce integration</li><li>Schema markup</li><li>Image SEO</li><li>Robots.txt editor</li><li>SEO audit checklist</li><li>Integration with webmaster tools (Google Analytics, Google Webmaster Tools, Google Search Console Bing Webmaster Tools, etc.)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>While the free version comes with a comprehensive feature set, we recommend you <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">upgrade to the paid version</a> for more functionality. If that sounds interesting, you can check out how to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">install and activate the premium version</a> of AIOSEO in this guide.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, if you’re <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/migrating-from-yoast-seo-to-all-in-one-seo/\" title=\"Migrating From Yoast SEO to All in One SEO (2 Simple Steps)\">migrating from another SEO plugin</a>, you can easily import all your data and settings to AIOSEO. This makes the transition seamless.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re looking for the best free WordPress plugins for your site, there’s no better place to start than with AIOSEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. <a aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpforms-lite/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">WPForms</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img width=\"795\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpforms.png\" alt=\"wpforms-best-form-builder-plugin\" class=\"wp-image-12382\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpforms.png 795w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpforms-600x302.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpforms-300x151.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpforms-768x386.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpforms-497x250.png 497w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpforms-100x50.png 100w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpforms-150x75.png 150w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpforms-200x101.png 200w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpforms-450x226.png 450w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>WPForms is the most beginner-friendly WordPress contact form plugin. It lets you create and add a contact form on your website in just a few clicks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It also comes with dozens of useful addons to add more features to your WordPress forms. WPForms offers 100+ form templates to create other types of forms, including appointment booking forms, simple order forms with payments, survey forms, newsletter forms, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It features a drag-and-drop form builder for easy customization. You can use the builder to add and customize your form fields without editing any code.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also use WPForms to add a payment form easily. It integrates with popular payment solutions like PayPal, Stripe, and Authorize.net to collect payments online.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>other features you&#8217;ll enjoy with WPForms Lite that you won&#8217;t find in many form builders include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Form revisions</li><li>Spam prevention</li><li>Unlimited number of forms</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>WPForms is easy to embed in your blog posts, pages, sidebar, footer, and other widget areas. It&#8217;s definitely the ultimate solution to adding and managing forms in WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. <a aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-analytics-for-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">MonsterInsights</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"198\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-free-wordpress-plugins-monsterinsights.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights is the best wordpress plugin for google analytics.\" class=\"wp-image-99986\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-free-wordpress-plugins-monsterinsights.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-free-wordpress-plugins-monsterinsights-300x85.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-free-wordpress-plugins-monsterinsights-600x170.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a aria-label=\"MonsterInsights (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-analytics-for-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">MonsterInsights</a> is the best WordPress Google Analytics plugin. It shows you real-time website traffic, actionable insights, and complete analytics within your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can track pages, posts, and campaigns to take quick action and grow your website. It also automatically tracks clicks on your affiliate links, email links, and all other outbound links.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you run an online store, then MonsterInsights can also track your:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Total revenue</li><li>Conversion rate</li><li>Average order value (AOV)</li><li>Top referral sources</li><li>And more </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>MonsterInsights also lets you create custom reports to find out more about your users and take the right action at the right time. With custom reports, you can identify the best time to publish an article, find the most popular categories, and learn about your top-scoring keywords.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>MonsterInsights has over 3 million active installations, making it your top choice to install and use for the growth of your business.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>4. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/coming-soon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">SeedProd</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img width=\"706\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/best-free-wordpress-plugins-seedprod.png\" alt=\"SeedProd is another plugin that should rank high on any best free WordPress plugin list.\" class=\"wp-image-99505\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/best-free-wordpress-plugins-seedprod.png 706w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/best-free-wordpress-plugins-seedprod-300x170.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/best-free-wordpress-plugins-seedprod-600x340.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 706px) 100vw, 706px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/coming-soon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">SeedProd</a> is another invaluable WordPress plugin you should consider. It’s a powerful drag-and-drop page builder that makes it easy for anyone to build beautiful websites. That’s why over 1 million websites trust it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>SeedProd allows you to easily customize your website’s theme so your website looks professional. The plugin also helps you build:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Custom sites&nbsp;</li><li>Landing pages</li><li>Sales funnels</li><li>Coming soon pages</li><li>And more</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the biggest advantages of SeedProd is that it’s one of the best WordPress themes for SEO. This results in ultra-fast sites that meet Google’s Page Experience standards. Fast-loading sites also result in better user experience (UX) and improved conversions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another much-loved feature of SeedProd is that it’s a no-code page builder. This means anyone can build beautiful websites without any technical knowledge. All this is made possible by the 150+ templates for every kind of page you may want to build. If you’re up to it, you can even build custom pages and themes from scratch.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>5. <a aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-mail-smtp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">WP Mail SMTP</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img width=\"795\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpmailsmtp.png\" alt=\"WP Mail SMTP best wordpress plugins\" class=\"wp-image-12384\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpmailsmtp.png 795w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpmailsmtp-600x302.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpmailsmtp-300x151.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpmailsmtp-768x386.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpmailsmtp-497x250.png 497w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpmailsmtp-100x50.png 100w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpmailsmtp-150x75.png 150w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpmailsmtp-200x101.png 200w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wpmailsmtp-450x226.png 450w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Have you ever had problems with WordPress not sending emails?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress has to be able to send emails out like password reset emails (in case you forget your login), contact form notifications, important update reminders, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But by default, WordPress uses a method (the <code>wp_mail()</code> function) that doesn&#8217;t always work, because it gets blocked by spam filters.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s where SMTP comes in. It&#8217;s a bett