w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nextiva-450x226.png 450w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/nextiva/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Nextiva</a> is the best business phone service in the industry. It enables remote teams to work from anywhere and stay connected to a reliable network.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It offers phone, email, SMS, and live chat services on one platform. The features include audio and video conferencing, helpdesk software, sales CRM, unlimited calling, toll-free number, auto-attendant, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also keep a record of your communication with call recording and rating options. It provides real-time analytics and custom reports on your dashboard.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nextiva integrates with popular services and business applications to add more features to your phone system. It also offers real-time disaster recovery and call-forwarding features to stay available all the time.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Constant Contact</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"795\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/constantcontact.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12405\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/constantcontact.png 795w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/constantcontact-600x302.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/constantcontact-300x151.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/constantcontact-768x386.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/constantcontact-497x250.png 497w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/constantcontact-100x50.png 100w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/constantcontact-150x75.png 150w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/constantcontact-200x101.png 200w, https://aios